comment: Lala Lala Song 2018 AHS (Long Official Versión Studio)
Playing this as I walk down the hallway to my class.
Cordelia was the best figure ever. How she emerged from unsecured hopeless woman to strong powerful individual.

Ugh it's sad to see this season is already over. This one really stuck with me because Coven is my absolute favorite season and honestly it deserves it's own spin off. Getting to see my favorite witches back in action was so nostalgic.
